metadata.name: TryColor #1
metadata.description:
TryColour is a NFT work created by manga artist Shunpei Dozono (@10000syunpay).
Our ultimate goal for TryColour is to create a board game using the world and characters of TryColour.

We consider the following as purchase benefits.

(1) Invitation to the discord.
(2) Naming rights for the character you purchase (to the extent that the worldview is not destroyed).
(3) " A little fancy " physical artwork.

Let's build the board game together!
